{"tid":997230,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"習近平：無論將來中國怎麼發展，都「永遠」屬於發展中國家","createTime":"2019-01-27T04:00:43.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-04T01:08:02.000Z","uid":155095,"like":5,"dislike":107,"uniUserReply":47,"replies":[{"pid":"165020f1bef2a1531ac719f8fcc038202b6f8b69","tid":997230,"uid":155095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-27T04:00:43.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\">習近平指出，當今世界正處於大發展大變革大調整時期，新興市場國家和發展中國家面臨共同的機遇和挑戰。新興市場國家和發展中國家加強團結合作愈顯重要。<br />\n<br />\n習近平強調，中國特色社會主義進入了新時代，<span style=\"color: red;\">同時中國是世界上<strong>最大發展中國家</strong>的地位沒有變。無論將來中國怎麼發展，都<strong>永遠屬於發展中國家</strong></span>，都會堅定支持廣大發展中國家發展，都會繼續致力於同大家發展緊密的伙伴關係。我們要以&ldquo;金磚+&rdquo;合作為平台，同心協力，砥礪奮進，攜手推動新興市場國家和發展中國家在共同發展中取得更大成就。</span><br />\n<br />\nsource: <a href=\"https://finance.sina.cn/china/gncj/2018-07-27/detail-ihfxsxzf5105721.d.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffinance.sina.cn%2Fchina%2Fgncj%2F2018-07-27%2Fdetail-ihfxsxzf5105721.d.html&d=S7XkTtUUaO0bij%2BLmYwwlNU7RO4jIL0fLOArxO5LqtQ%3D&h=cc597ef3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://finance.sina.cn/china/gncj/2018-07-27/detail-ihfxsxzf5105721.d.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://aboutchinablog.files.wordpress.com/2018/07/screenshot_20180729233259.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Faboutchinablog.files.wordpress.com%2F2018%2F07%2Fscreenshot_20180729233259.jpg&h=a1db6111&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/70E10pA.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F70E10pA.png&h=dd02683f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong>負責任的大國，領會總書記的責任觀</strong><br />\n<br />\n進入21世紀以來，我國支付聯合國會費增加了12倍<br />\n<br />\n我國在五常中對聯合國維和活動的貢獻最大<br />\n<br />\n我國引領或積極參加朝核、伊核與敘利亞化武及其他地區熱點問題的和平解決<br />\n<br />\n我國對發展中國家援助表現卓越2012年:我國對亞洲經濟增長的貢獻率達到50% <br />\n<br />\n我國對綠色能源發展投資做多我國對關於全球氣候變化的國際合作更為積極<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://slidesplayer.com/slide/11398204/61/images/18/领会总书记的责任观+进入21世纪以来，我国支付联合国会费增加了12倍+我国在五常中对联合国维和活动的贡献最大.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fslidesplayer.com%2Fslide%2F11398204%2F61%2Fimages%2F18%2F%E9%A2%86%E4%BC%9A%E6%80%BB%E4%B9%A6%E8%AE%B0%E7%9A%84%E8%B4%A3%E4%BB%BB%E8%A7%82%2B%E8%BF%9B%E5%85%A521%E4%B8%96%E7%BA%AA%E4%BB%A5%E6%9D%A5%EF%BC%8C%E6%88%91%E5%9B%BD%E6%94%AF%E4%BB%98%E8%81%94%E5%90%88%E5%9B%BD%E4%BC%9A%E8%B4%B9%E5%A2%9E%E5%8A%A0%E4%BA%8612%E5%80%8D%2B%E6%88%91%E5%9B%BD%E5%9C%A8%E4%BA%94%E5%B8%B8%E4%B8%AD%E5%AF%B9%E8%81%94%E5%90%88%E5%9B%BD%E7%BB%B4%E5%92%8C%E6%B4%BB%E5%8A%A8%E7%9A%84%E8%B4%A1%E7%8C%AE%E6%9C%80%E5%A4%A7.jpg&h=8a8035ca&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"6f901c7f02b824247597372d3cb302790085a3dd","tid":997230,"uid":55941,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-27T04:01:53.000Z","msg":".......................................................................<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"78d3ebd09f7d32a94c7e8aa136b63c7df270af9b","tid":997230,"uid":16250,"like":81,"dislike":2,"score":79,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-27T04:02:52.000Z","msg":"小學程度係咁上下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"24e13200fb24b4a7d6f76d89156336831b26e3b2","tid":997230,"uid":44916,"like":40,"dislike":0,"score":40,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-27T04:03:36.000Z","msg":"發展<span style=\"color: red;\">中國</span>家"},{"pid":"0cafc7ff3a346ecc022128b314ad2e0d61e48498","tid":997230,"uid":56957,"like":70,"dislike":0,"score":70,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-27T04:06:57.000Z","msg":"人無恥<br />\n便無敵"},{"pid":"bc531629b345faa65ece8194702172cc804d9fbf","tid":997230,"uid":10692,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-27T04:07:41.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c76a916cc9807bb803739227aeb441d4d2d7abf2","tid":997230,"uid":121146,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-27T04:08:36.000Z","msg":"咁炸返去做發展中囉 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bf9722699d503ec4