moji\" />"},{"pid":"abedd3c6b772d60e901929c37aae4db28bcfe153","tid":997230,"uid":18127,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-27T04:26:44.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"fff87e296e8483419ff98b280cf313ddf472fd3d","tid":997230,"uid":99205,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-27T04:28:32.000Z","msg":"將結束法國和意大利訪問的中國國務委員兼外長王毅，周五（25日）評論近來電訊巨頭華為等中國企業風波。他表示，在沒有任何證據下，「<span style=\"color: red;\">動用國家力量來抹黑和打擊特定的企業，這種作法既不公正，也不道德。</span>」<br />\n<br />\n王毅指，更不能接受事件背後顯而易見的政治意圖和政治操弄，認為各國該對這種無理做法和霸凌行徑，予以警惕和抵制。<br />\n<br />\n他續說，各國皆有維護國家信息安全的權利，但不能打着「安全的幌子」，以莫須有的借口，損害甚至扼殺企業的正當合法經營。<br />\n<br />\n呢個國家(得共產黨一個執政黨)<br />\n真係去到cls既地步"},{"pid":"81bc294f6794d6eb2e9c117c063b3febcb57ce6f","tid":997230,"uid":15815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-27T04:29:48.000Z","msg":"自爆幾個核彈再講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eefeef030c8ad90b62369f0e0a787f8b73a92028","tid":997230,"uid":2383,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-27T04:33:56.000Z","msg":"小支支<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0d20406a441520fcf1075d586a73d6eae009d814","tid":997230,"uid":70786,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-27T04:35:32.000Z","msg":"回帶嘅<br />\n仲以為佢又咁夠膽出嚟吠<br />\n原來仲匿緊係黨媒同華春蠅個閪入面"},{"pid":"f96b188e59a27cb3ed7cecab7f2ef6be31a44aed","tid":997230,"uid":81190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-27T04:35:51.000Z","msg":"意思姐係想做無賴？<br />\n愈講愈衰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"26fde7df402f747747110c8db17f55a2fd4733b4","tid":997230,"uid":155095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-27T10:30:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5b7b985b4f69c076297d92c367a652b18c8a1bc2","tid":997230,"uid":54337,"like":0,"dislike":0,